The device chosen for the current homework is a modified crankshaft.
It is capable of transmitting a vertical motion by obtaining the horizontal motion of a piston.

<a href="https://github.com/gabrielesala/">
  <img src="https://github.com/gabrielesala/meccanismo_di_spinta/blob/main/meccanismo_di_spinta.svg" width="100%" height="144">
</a>

Constrains:
- α >= 0
- Lm, Lb, Hp > 0
- Lm Sin(α) < Lb
- Lm Cos(α) > 1/2 Hp

